%h1 FlippyWindow
.introduction
  %p.introduction__blurb FlippyWindow is a simple Windows application that non-destructively flips any part of your screen horizontally, in real-time and using minimal resources.
  .introduction__screenshot-with-arrow
    %img{:alt => "A screenshot of FlippyWindow in action.", :src => "https://www.robotinaponcho.net/flippywindow/screenshot.png", :title => "A screenshot of FlippyWindow in action."}
  %p.introduction__blurb.introduction__blurb--more Flipping images (or viewing things with a mirror) is a technique used to <a href="http://yourfirstproduct.com/info/bmreverse">help view things with "fresh eyes"</a> which can aid with <a href="http://www.comic-tools.com/2008/10/my-mirror-is-most-important.html">spotting visual issues</a>.
.download
  %h2.download__button
    %a.download__button__link#itch{:href => "https://damiendart.itch.io/flippywindow"} Download<span class="collapsable"> FlippyWindow</span> from <img alt="itch.io" src="https://www.robotinaponcho.net/assets/itchio.svg" title="itch.io">
  %ul.download__information-list
    %li.download__information-list__item
      %strong Requires Windows 8 or later.
    %li.download__information-list__item Nothing to install; just unzip and run<span class="collapsable"> the executable</a></span>.
